            ],
            "text": "In Tian Xia, the underwater nation of Xidao lies in the shallow gulf between Minkai and the mainland. Though the nation-states that make up Xidao are independent, athamarus comprise the majority of the population and are in charge for all practical purposes. Stone obelisks called trade spires reach above the surface of the gulf to collect offerings from travelers. Athamarus monitor these and guide or trade with those who donate.",
            "type": "section"
          }
        ],
        "sources": [
